passages.text:
**end
@eon_excited_lion
There you are, at the end of the game.
It was quite a journey.
[[Lion|Sad]]
passages.name: End

passages.text:
**brokenHeart
@eon_depressed_ox
It might be scary when things come to an end. 
Ends involve goodbye's. And they are hard.
[[Ox|Gift]]
passages.name: Sad

passages.text:
**trophy
@eon_flirting_human
But remember, it is the goodbye itself that makes everything itself worth.
Maybe you collected all the special gifts. They'll stick with you forever.
Or maybe, you missed opportunities. That's okay to. The journey was the main gift. 
And you had it. No one can take it away from you.
[[Human|Bye]]
passages.name: Gift

passages.text:
**bluePlanet
@eon_hi_eagle
And as you say goodbye, remember that all that experience is uniquely yours.
As they say, "No one else can feel it for you. Only you can let it in."
Farewell visitor! Wishing you the greatest of adventures!
passages.name: Bye
